extends ../layouts/default

block head
  meta(property="og:title"        content="Register now for Spring League!")
  meta(property="og:url"          content="http://www.sflultimate.com/register")
  meta(property="og:description"  content="Regular registration closes February 13th, so be sure to sign up today to avoid the late registration price of $65!")

  meta(property="og:image"        content="http://www.sflultimate.com/images/open-graph/registration.jpg")
  meta(property="og:image:width"  content="1200")
  meta(property="og:image:height" content="630")

block content
  .container: .row: .col-sm-10.col-sm-offset-1.col-md-8.col-md-offset-2
    h1 2016 Fall League Registration

    h3 Summary

    p This fall we'll be back at Amelia Earhart Park, just off I-95 at Ives Dairy Road.
    iframe(src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d14358.205887616712!2d-80.2784486!3d25.8842357!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0x5fd60d3c7189a581!2sAmelia+Earhart+Park!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sus!4v1475028057840" width="100%" height="300" frameborder="0" style="border:0" allowfullscreen)
    p Regular season games will be <strong>Tuesday evenings at 8pm, starting October 4th</strong>. We're planning on 9 weeks of play, skipping the Tuesday of Thanksgiving Weekend. <strong>Finals are still being determined, and will be</strong> at Amelia Earhart Park.

    p Registration is open <strong>as of September 28th</strong> and the costs are:
    ul
      li $30 for students
      li $50 for everyone else
    p The fee includes the games, playoffs & events.  Late registration (at a $65 fee for everyone, as space permits) will continue until after the first week of play.

    hr

    h3 Registration

    .alert.alert-info
      strong Refund Policy: 
      | Should there be an error in your registration (paid for a youth fee when an adult or vice versa), we will provide a refund.  Otherwise we will not be providing refunds.

    form#registration(action="register" method="post" autocomplete="off")
      if err
        .alert.alert-danger
          strong Error: 
          span=err
      input#user_id.form-control.hidden(type='user_id' autocomplete='false' name='user_id' placeholder='' value=formData.user_id)
      .row
        .col-xs-6
          .form-group
            label(for='firstName') First Name
            input#firstName.form-control(type='text' name='name.first' placeholder='' value=formData['name.first'] required)
        .col-xs-6
          .form-group
            label(for='lastName') Last Name
            input#lastName.form-control(type='text' name='name.last' placeholder='' value=formData['name.last'] required)

      //- Email
      .form-group
        label(for='email') Email address
        input#email.form-control(type='email' name='email'   placeholder='' value=formData.email required)

      //- Pairing
      .form-group
        label(for='partner') Partner<br><small>If you would like to pair up with another player for sign-up, write their name here.</small>
        input#partner.form-control(type='partner' autocomplete='false' name='partner' placeholder='' value=formData.partner)
        input#partner_id.form-control.hidden(type='partner_id' autocomplete='false' name='partner_id' placeholder='' value=formData.partner_id)

      //- Age Group
      #age
        label Are you a:
          .radio
            label
              input(type='radio' name='age' value='Adult')
              |     Adult
          .radio
            label
              input(type='radio' name='age' value='Student')
              |     Student

      //- Participation
      label(for="participation" name="participation") Expected Attendance

      p
        small Knowing how often you plan on being there helps captains pick well-rounded teams

      select#participation.form-control(name="participation" value=formData.participation)
        option(value="30") Less than 30%
        option(value="50") Around 50%
        option(value="80" selected="selected") Greater than 80%
      br

      //- Shirt Size
      label(for="shirtSize" name="shirtSize") Shirt Size
      select#shirtSize.form-control(name="shirtSize" value=formData.shirtSize)
        option(value="S") S
        option(value="M") M
        option(value="L") L
        option(value="XL") XL
        option(value="XXL") XXL
      br

      //- Skill Level
      label(for="skillLevel" name="skillLevel") Skill Level
      select#skillLevel.form-control(name="skillLevel" value=formData.skillLevel)
        option(value='1') 1 - Absolute Beginner
        option(value='2') 2 - Hey wait, what's a flick?
        option(value='3') 3 - Working on throws, basic knowledge of game
        option(value='4') 4 - Pickup player, okay throws
        option(value='5') 5 - Decent backhand & forehand. Little to no club experience
        option(value='6') 6 - Fairly solid backhand & forehand. Some club experience
        option(value='7') 7 - Tourney experience. Several years of club
        option(value='8') 8 - Club level, solid all around, not prone to errors
        option(value='9') 9 - Rock star. spot on throws, awesome D

      br
      h3 Waiver
      .checkbox
        label
          input(type='checkbox', value='' required)
          | I agree to SFLUltimate's <a data-toggle="modal" data-target="#waiver">terms & conditions</a>.

      h3 Payment Information
      #payment-form
      .text-center
        button.btn.btn-default.btn-lg.btn-primary(type='submit') Submit

